@startuml AD_D04_Request_Lab_Test_Review_Results

title AD_D04 — Request Lab Test & Review Results

|Doctor|
|System|
|Lab Technician|

|Doctor|

note
  Prerequisites:
  - Doctor is authenticated
  - Patient is assigned to this doctor
  - Lab test catalogue is configured
end note

start

:Open patient profile;
:Navigate to Lab Tests section;
:Click "Request New Test";

|System|

:Display test catalogue\n(filterable by category);

|Doctor|

:Select test(s) from catalogue;
:Set priority: Routine or Urgent;
:Add clinical instructions\n(e.g., fasting required, notes for lab);

|System|

if (All required fields complete?) then (no)
  :Highlight missing fields;
  |Doctor|
  :Complete missing fields;
  |System|
else (yes)
endif

:Create test order linked to:\n- Patient record\n- Doctor ID\n- Priority + instructions;
:Notify Lab Technician of new order;

|Lab Technician|

:Process test order;
:Upload result + flag if abnormal;

|System|

:Link result to patient record\nand original doctor order;

if (Result abnormal / critical?) then (yes)
  :Trigger critical alert to doctor\n(in-system + email);
else (no)
  :Send standard result-ready\nnotification to doctor;
endif

|Doctor|

:Open patient profile;\nNavigate to test results;

|System|

:Display result report\nlinked to the original order;

|Doctor|

:Review full result report;
:Acknowledge result;

|System|

:Record acknowledgement:\ntimestamp + doctor ID;

stop

@enduml
